Package: ppml
Title: Poisson Pseudo Maximum Likelihood Estimator
Version: 0.1
Date: 2019-08-01
Authors@R: person(given = "Lukas", family = "Kleinheinz", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "lukas.kleinheinz@student.uibk.ac.at")
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: sandwich, lmtest
Description: Can be used to estimate gravity models using the glm function of stats with the quasipoisson distribution, a log-link and heteroskedasticity robust standard errors. The robust standard errors are calculated with the sandwich and coeftest package. 
Author: Lukas Kleinheinz [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Lukas Kleinheinz <lukas.kleinheinzk@student.uibk.ac.at>
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3


